Tanasha Donna says it has not been easy raising her son alone. Tanasha and Diamond separated, leaving her a single mother providing for her son, Naseeb Junior. While celebrating finally moving to a new house, the singer assured her son she would do anything for him to live well. "@naseeb.junior your laugh is infectious my son," she wrote on Instagram. "Glad you love your new home. Your momma works day and night to make sure you good, and she’s only getting started. Trust me. "It’s never easy doing it alone, the pressure is real but so worth it, and as long as I’m alive, you will never lack. I promise you. Alhamdulillah. Allah is on our side." Edited by T Jalio